                    For capped sectors (hospitality, trucking, retail), Saskatchewan will operate
                    <strong>six scheduled intake windows</strong> throughout 2026. Applicants in these
                    sectors can only apply during the final six months of their work permit validity.
                    Priority sectors maintain year-round continuous intake.
                </p>

